{"tid":664310,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【5月14日軍史上的今天】德軍轟炸鹿特丹 荷蘭投降","createTime":"2018-05-14T03:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T09:20:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"145d35b9ccc9357b9358fff21740302ac05cbf97","tid":664310,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T03:46:45.000Z","msg":"1940年5月14日，納粹德軍轟炸荷蘭第二大城鹿特丹，造成超過800名平民喪生，荷蘭政府為避免更多平民傷亡，選擇向德軍投降。<br />\n<br />\n納粹德軍5月10日入侵荷蘭，初期進展順利，後卻受到荷軍頑強抵抗，希特勒因而命令德國空軍協助地面部隊「迅速擊潰荷蘭要塞」。德軍原以轟炸作為對鹿特丹守軍的威脅，結果因協調失誤，已起飛的德國空軍轟炸機未接收到行動延遲命令，仍對鹿特丹市內進行轟炸，超過800人死亡、8萬人無家可歸。<br />\n<br />\n由於荷蘭空軍已失去作戰能力，防空部隊也不足，荷蘭政府決定停止抵抗。雖然德軍迅速贏得荷蘭戰役，但盟軍也因此解除對德國民生城市的轟炸限制，最後有50萬德國平民在二戰的盟軍戰略轟炸中喪生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wiEYHsVSgK1xgZ6GIYRKCQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/youthdailynews_517/bbac3741aa2fd4f0d48bb80f74654829\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FwiEYHsVSgK1xgZ6GIYRKCQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fyouthdailynews_517%2Fbbac3741aa2fd4f0d48bb80f74654829&h=ae853236&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n納粹德軍轟炸荷蘭鹿特丹，迫使該國政府投降。圖為遭轟炸的鹿特丹。（取自德國聯邦檔案館網站）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/5%E6%9C%8814%E6%97%A5%E8%BB%8D%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9-%E5%BE%B7%E8%BB%8D%E8%BD%9F%E7%82%B8%E9%B9%BF%E7%89%B9%E4%B8%B9-%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E6%8A%95%E9%99%8D-160000984.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F5%25E6%259C%258814%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%258F%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E8%25BB%258D%25E8%25BD%259F%25E7%2582%25B8%25E9%25B9%25BF%25E7%2589%25B9%25E4%25B8%25B9-%25E8%258D%25B7%25E8%2598%25AD%25E6%258A%2595%25E9%2599%258D-160000984.html&d=BzsFvvO4moS6CNL1%2FM7kiBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=574d9451\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/5%E6%9C%8814%E6%97%A5%E8%BB%8D%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9-%E5%BE%B7%E8%BB%8D%E8%BD%9F%E7%82%B8%E9%B9%BF%E7%89%B9%E4%B8%B9-%E8%8D%B7%E8%98%AD%E6%8A%95%E9%99%8D-160000984.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f005e78cb6c7b74e6bdb8ab098ec061d1bdf03ac","tid":664310,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T09:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}